<br>
I'm a Gnome on Rallos.  I was getting in a huge /ooc argument with a horrible PKer named Lilbutcher, who was killing all the newbies and then consoling them with shouts like &quot;I'm sorry you died, Waxwing, but this is Rallos, and you have to get used to it!&quot;  Cripes if that isn't the worst excuse for murdering newbies I ever heard--it's not me killing you, it's the server.  I'm really doing you a FAVOR by killing you so young and looting your newbie tunic, since you need to learn how to die anyway.<br>
<br>
So I just HAD to tell the whole world how lame I thought this guy was.  <br>
<br>
Anyway, later that day I'm running to the warrior's guild in Ak'Anon to finish up the Bootstrutter's Backpack quest.  It's a great newby item--10 slot backpack, 10% weight reduction, but the quest is kind of a pain.  You have to run all over Ak'Anon delivering cards to these four spiders, but only 3 of them ever seem to be spawned at one time.  Then you have to deliver a box to a guy named Joogl out by the windmills in Steamfont, but he's dead most of the time because necros and druids love to camp him.  Anyway, he gives you a note to take to the warrior's merchant in Ak'Anon, and half the time that merchant will give you the Bootstrutter's quest and a rat named Duster X will spawn who you have to kill to get the pack.  The other half the time he gives you another quest, and you have to start all over again from scratch.<br>
<br>
So I'm running back with the note from Joogl, and I hear somebody running behind me:  it's Lilbutcher!  Eeps.  I stop and hit hide and hope he sees my ghost running off into the sunset.  He must because he keeps running past me, and I follow him.  <br>
<br>
It turns out he's doing the same quest I'm doing!  I overhear him give the note to the warrior merchant, and the merchant hands him the Bootstrutter's quest.  <br>
<br>
Thinking quickly, I wheel around and rush off to the far end of Ak'Anon where Duster X spawns.  I find him and kill him quick and loot the corpse.  Then I sit down and hide.  Before long Lilbutcher comes running by.  <br>
<br>
I let him run around for a while, and then send him a /tell.<br>
<br>
Me:  &quot;You're not looking for Duster X are you, Lilbutcher?&quot;<br>
Lilbutcher: &quot;Yes!  Why?&quot;<br>
Me:  &quot;Some necro just blasted him.  He seemed really happy about it.&quot;<br>
Lilbutcher: &quot;*Grrr*  It's taken me two hours to get him to spawn!&quot;<br>
Me:  &quot;Gee, that's tough.  Wish I got the necro's name.  He's like level 40, though.&quot;<br>
Lilbutcher:  &quot;*Grrr* nm then.&quot;<br>
Me:  &quot;But I have a copy of the note you need to get Bootstrutters.  I've already got one so it's no good to me.  Want to buy it?&quot;<br>
Lilbutcher:  &quot;Hmmm...how much?&quot;<br>
<br>
And I sold him the note for 5gg!  And now Lilbutcher thinks I'm a great guy!<br>
<br>
Ha ha ha ha ha ha.  It's fun being a rogue.<br>
<br>
Caper the Sometimes Surprising Deep Muse<br>
Low level Rogue Rallos Zek. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylia>Cylia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/26/00 2:21:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=520.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://austriangothic.rip.at/cyliaphoto.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My first truly Rogueish act.</span><hr size=1> LOL <p><p><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="3"><b>I got a Text sig now, everyone
